    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="How to Import Assets in C4 PTR" class="article-title">
          How to Import Assets in C4 PTR
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2026-06-02T20:03:48Z" title="2026-06-02T20:03:48Z" data-datetime="relative">June 02, 2026 20:03</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/52243667123603-How-to-Import-Assets-in-C4-PTR/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>Before you can use your ships and resources in C4 PTR, you need to import them into the game through the <strong>Port of Entry</strong>.</p><p>In PTR, assets are provided for testing purposes. These are not real assets</p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4HQ17F9PN765HVDZPVGPA8">Step 1: Open the Port of Entry</h2><p>After creating your C4 PTR profile, you will arrive on the main map.</p><p>To start importing your assets:</p><ol>
<li data-list-item-id="e03ce585058ff3b16bcd29cf0fb30d62a">
<p>Look at the bottom-right corner of the map.</p>
<figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 1578/1030;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52243683453587" width="1578" height="1030"></figure>
</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e3dedfcc89f0f14ca67fd34a6e20cb3c1">Click the <strong>Port of Entry</strong>.</li>
</ol><p>The Port of Entry is where you can move your provided PTR assets into the game.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4HQ3H0KTQ6RXACQ0Z33SAK">Step 2: Select the assets you want to import</h2><p>Inside the import interface, you will see the available items that can be imported.</p><p>To select your assets:</p><ol>
<li data-list-item-id="e0dbdbfbf8e8cd0297d3ee80a6ef1a8f1">
<p>Click <strong>MAX</strong> on the right side of each item you want to import.</p>
<figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 1660/976;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52243683457043" width="1660" height="976"></figure>
</li>
<li data-list-item-id="ec1758f830fe1f5a3b819d36265f0459d">
<p>Click <strong>Deposit</strong> next to each selected item.</p>
<figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 1655/974;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52243683457427" width="1655" height="974"></figure>
</li>
</ol><p>This will move the selected items into the manifest on the right side of the screen.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4HQ66PXZR3G6HR2CDYJXY5">Step 3: Review the transfer manifest</h2><p>After selecting your assets, review the manifest on the right side of the interface.</p><p>The manifest shows which assets are ready to be transferred into the game.</p><p>Before continuing, make sure the items you want to import are listed there.</p><figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 1044/1110;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52243683457683" width="1044" height="1110"></figure><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4HQ7J9F3HYXJ6JKADPCZNX">Step 4: Transfer the manifest</h2><p>Once your manifest is ready:</p><ol>
<li data-list-item-id="e35f6a783b881f37e5fb0e861cbad998e">
<p>Click <strong>Transfer Manifest</strong> at the top of the manifest box.</p>
<figure class="wysiwyg-image"><img style="aspect-ratio: 1026/105;" src="/hc/article_attachments/52243683458451" width="1026" height="105"></figure>
</li>
<li data-list-item-id="eaffb886e718ab4b01933b5a52343480a">Wait for the transfer to complete.</li>
</ol><p>After the transfer is complete, your assets will be imported into your faction CSS.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><h2 id="h_01KT4HPM39R4D7V3XK8ZDWS7VG">&nbsp;</h2><h2 id="h_01KT4HQBM1VSCBM6EPBXZGGMQW">Where are imported assets sent?</h2><p>Imported assets are sent to your faction CSS.</p><p>The CSS is the only base that has a Port of Entry for import and export.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4HQE0HRW0W948ZY2WH2ZZY">Important notes</h2><ul>
<li data-list-item-id="ee7ff022b8d68613c67abe2533627f136">PTR assets are provided for testing and are not real assets.</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e387b1003920073c9e554659af497ec3e">You need to import your assets before you can use them in C4 PTR.</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e40a2a0ddcaa40286dcce331283e759ed">The import process in PTR is expected to be similar to the mainnet process, although the PTR remains a test environment and may change over time.</li>
<li data-list-item-id="e0c13bc90f6f393a89eeaafed0a00a13b">Your imported assets will be available from your faction CSS.</li>
</ul><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p><h2 id="h_01KT4HQH03QQEJD3FQB8YWZA7N">What to do next</h2><p>Once your assets are imported, you can start using them in C4 PTR.</p><p>Recommended next steps:</p><ul>
<li data-list-item-id="e74e07a16f48c5f4f91114d0f2745e5c9"><a href="/hc/en-us/articles/52243941755923">Learn how to use the C4 PTR map.</a></li>
<li data-list-item-id="e97ced8c269ee2a63a8e6ad24d43981ba"><a href="/hc/en-us/articles/52244580822419">Review the main menus.</a></li>
<li data-list-item-id="e02f231bc102546ee393296ec9cd80c8f"><a href="/hc/en-us/articles/52251721868563">Create or manage fleets.</a></li>
<li data-list-item-id="e2957363813892bd53c08466d3e86855c">Start exploring the available PTR systems.</li>
</ul></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

